snippet.title: Pathankot Terrorist Attack: Documents Related to Jaish-e-Mohammed Recovered from Car

localized.description:
Pathankot terror attack: Documents related to Jaish-e-Mohammed recovered from car used by militants.

Five terrorists and two soldiers killed in terror attack at Pathankot Air Force Station in Punjab. Pathankot is a key air base for MiG-21 Bison fighters and Mi-35 attack helicopters, located 50 kilometers from Indo-Pak border. The suspected terrorists belong to Jaish-e-Mohammed (JeM) terror outfit.
